sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant CLI as vnm render --style sketch
  participant RN as renderer<br/>(svg.ts · native · vnmRuntime)
  participant RG as src/rough<br/>(seeded generator)
  participant FT as sketch-font<br/>(Kalam base64)
  User->>CLI: render diagram.mmd --style sketch
  CLI->>RN: renderX({ style: "sketch" })
  RN->>RG: roughShape / roughPolyline / openArrowhead (seed = node/edge id)
  RG-->>RN: wobbly path d-strings (deterministic, no RNG)
  RN->>FT: sketchFontFaceCss() + family
  FT-->>RN: @font-face (base64 data URI) + font-family
  RN-->>CLI: SVG - rough shapes + open arrowheads + embedded font
  Note over RN: PNG → resvg registers the Kalam buffer · HTML/interactive → vnmRuntime inlines the SAME rough gen (byte-parity guard)
